text: Stephen Beatty (born 11 April 1959) is a Canadian rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Canada Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:People from Woodstock, Ontario
